    "TranscriptEntries": "[{\"SpeakerId\":\"1afed000000LztJAAS\",\"SpeakerRole\":\"EndUser\",\"EntryStartTime\":1767613219379,\"EntryEndTime\":1767613231959,\"Duration\":12,\"Sequence\":0,\"Text\":\"Hey, Stephanie, I've been working on it. And I'll tell you my slides, two things about my slides. One, I didn't worry too much about font and about everything. I'm thinking more about delivery, et cetera.\"},{\"SpeakerId\":\"1afed000000LztJAAS\",\"SpeakerRole\":\"EndUser\",\"EntryStartTime\":1767613232839,\"EntryEndTime\":1767613244409,\"Duration\":11,\"Sequence\":1,\"Text\":\"And I use builds a lot when I present, but I don't use the build feature. I will take a slide and I will make, let's say, I have two builds in the slide.\"},{\"SpeakerId\":\"1afed000000LztJAAS\",\"SpeakerRole\":\"EndUser\",\"EntryStartTime\":1767613244429,\"EntryEndTime\":1767613251449,\"Duration\":7,\"Sequence\":2,\"Text\":\"I make three copies of the slide. I show the first part on slide one, the second part, Last part, Duke. third part slide three. So you'll get that when you see it.\"},{\"SpeakerId\":\"1afed000000LztJAAS\",\"SpeakerRole\":\"EndUser\",\"EntryStartTime\":1767613251469,\"EntryEndTime\":1767613264239,\"Duration\":12,\"Sequence\":3,\"Text\":\"That's the way that I would like for this to kind of go. Let's see. Also, I think the purpose here is just to make these slides kind of jump off the page as much as possible.\"},{\"SpeakerId\":\"1afed000000LztJAAS\",\"SpeakerRole\":\"EndUser\",\"EntryStartTime\":1767613264979,\"EntryEndTime\":1767613272039,\"Duration\":7,\"Sequence\":4,\"Text\":\"You know, good graphics, good, don't spend a lot of time on snazzing it up too much. I just wanted to make sure it looks professional.\"},{\"SpeakerId\":\"1afed000000LztJAAS\",\"SpeakerRole\":\"EndUser\",\"EntryStartTime\":1767613274059,\"EntryEndTime\":1767613286209,\"Duration\":12,\"Sequence\":5,\"Text\":\"The context of this is we're meeting with two people that we met with last week. And it's come to our attention that the demand for meal salt, they are not buying into our numbers.\"},{\"SpeakerId\":\"1afed000000LztJAAS\",\"SpeakerRole\":\"EndUser\",\"EntryStartTime\":1767613286249,\"EntryEndTime\":1767613294169,\"Duration\":7,\"Sequence\":6,\"Text\":\"So we're trying to tweak that, change it, and then show them the impact after the tweaks and changes. So that may help you a little bit.\"},{\"SpeakerId\":\"1afed000000LztJAAS\",\"SpeakerRole\":\"EndUser\",\"EntryStartTime\":1767613294269,\"EntryEndTime\":1767613302869,\"Duration\":8,\"Sequence\":7,\"Text\":\"So let me just kind of jump into it, and I'm going to run through it like I'm presenting. I think that will help you as far as how we...\"},{\"SpeakerId\":\"1afed000000LztJAAS\",\"SpeakerRole\":\"EndUser\",\"EntryStartTime\":1767613308359,\"EntryEndTime\":1767613312439,\"Duration\":4,\"Sequence\":8,\"Text\":\"Address is going forward. So let me show my screen.\"},{\"SpeakerId\":\"1afed000000LztJAAS\",\"SpeakerRole\":\"EndUser\",\"EntryStartTime\":1767613318109,\"EntryEndTime\":1767613333119,\"Duration\":15,\"Sequence\":9,\"Text\":\"Okay, so again we're meeting with two individuals and we only have 30 minutes and we got to get to the proposal piece, you know, fairly early maybe halfway through. So I'm just going to jump in.\"},{\"SpeakerId\":\"1afed000000LztJAAS\",\"SpeakerRole\":\"EndUser\",\"EntryStartTime\":1767613333279,\"EntryEndTime\":1767613346149,\"Duration\":12,\"Sequence\":10,\"Text\":\"So We wanted to recalibrate and meet again as we planned last week. And there's really three specific things that we want to address in this discussion. Number one, we want to rethink the demand.\"},{\"SpeakerId\":\"1afed000000LztJAAS\",\"SpeakerRole\":\"EndUser\",\"EntryStartTime\":1767613346169,\"EntryEndTime\":1767613355119,\"Duration\":8,\"Sequence\":11,\"Text\":\"We do a bunch of numbers that you last week. There were some questions around it and we want to go back and rethink that. Number two, we want to talk about the cost of doing nothing.\"},{\"SpeakerId\":\"1afed000000LztJAAS\",\"SpeakerRole\":\"EndUser\",\"EntryStartTime\":1767613355559,\"EntryEndTime\":1767613357619,\"Duration\":2,\"Sequence\":12,\"Text\":\"If you don't do anything and just continue as is.\"},{\"SpeakerId\":\"1afed000000LztJAAS\",\"SpeakerRole\":\"EndUser\",\"EntryStartTime\":1767613358949,\"EntryEndTime\":1767613359769,\"Duration\":0,\"Sequence\":13,\"Text\":\"What does that look like?\"},{\"SpeakerId\":\"1afed000000LztJAAS\",\"SpeakerRole\":\"EndUser\",\"EntryStartTime\":1767613359809,\"EntryEndTime\":1767613372529,\"Duration\":12,\"Sequence\":14,\"Text\":\"And number three, we want to present to you what we think are two viable win-win options, you know, as we go forward. So, So let's just jump right into it. So rethinking demand.\"},{\"SpeakerId\":\"1afed000000LztJAAS\",\"SpeakerRole\":\"EndUser\",\"EntryStartTime\":1767613372909,\"EntryEndTime\":1767613375089,\"Duration\":2,\"Sequence\":15,\"Text\":\"Why is it important for us to kind of rethink this?\"},{\"SpeakerId\":\"1afed000000LztJAAS\",\"SpeakerRole\":\"EndUser\",\"EntryStartTime\":1767613375869,\"EntryEndTime\":1767613384089,\"Duration\":8,\"Sequence\":16,\"Text\":\"If we don't agree on a minimal amount of demand and the cost associated with that demand over the next five years, and really none of this matters.\"},{\"SpeakerId\":\"1afed000000LztJAAS\",\"SpeakerRole\":\"EndUser\",\"EntryStartTime\":1767613384589,\"EntryEndTime\":1767613392379,\"Duration\":7,\"Sequence\":17,\"Text\":\"It doesn't matter if we have a number that's something and you have a number of something else, and everything we talk about is kind of irrelevant.\"},{\"SpeakerId\":\"1afed000000LztJAAS\",\"SpeakerRole\":\"EndUser\",\"EntryStartTime\":1767613392419,\"EntryEndTime\":1767613403369,\"Duration\":10,\"Sequence\":18,\"Text\":\"So we've got to drill down and agree on a minimal amount of a demand. Secondly, we're going to dig in and show you how we define the demand for the Mueller.\"},{\"SpeakerId\":\"1afed000000LztJAAS\",\"SpeakerRole\":\"EndUser\",\"EntryStartTime\":1767613404109,\"EntryEndTime\":1767613414409,\"Duration\":10,\"Sequence\":19,\"Text\":\"We went to a lot of effort to get there, and we're going to walk you through that. And the demand that we had was based on a mule and not on a just add.\"},{\"SpeakerId\":\"1afed000000LztJAAS\",\"SpeakerRole\":\"EndUser\",\"EntryStartTime\":1767613414529,\"EntryEndTime\":1767613418769,\"Duration\":4,\"Sequence\":20,\"Text\":\"So we had to do a bunch of detail work to get there.\"},{\"SpeakerId\":\"1afed000000LztJAAS\",\"SpeakerRole\":\"EndUser\",\"EntryStartTime\":1767613418849,\"EntryEndTime\":1767613422159,\"Duration\":3,\"Sequence\":21,\"Text\":\"So how do we define demand for the mule?\"},{\"SpeakerId\":\"1afed000000LztJAAS\",\"SpeakerRole\":\"EndUser\",\"EntryStartTime\":1767613422259,\"EntryEndTime\":1767613428059,\"Duration\":5,\"Sequence\":22,\"Text\":\"And you got to remember that when we are looking at a mule, there's a tremendous amount of risk for us involved there.\"},{\"SpeakerId\":\"1afed000000LztJAAS\",\"SpeakerRole\":\"EndUser\",\"EntryStartTime\":1767613428579,\"EntryEndTime\":1767613436739,\"Duration\":8,\"Sequence\":23,\"Text\":\"Because if we don't accurately identify demand and you far exceed it, then we're going to come out, come on the short end of that discussion.\"},{\"SpeakerId\":\"1afed000000LztJAAS\",\"SpeakerRole\":\"EndUser\",\"EntryStartTime\":1767613436819,\"EntryEndTime\":1767613446229,\"Duration\":9,\"Sequence\":24,\"Text\":\"So what we did was we went to every identified stakeholder of every identified project that we can find that is using meal self.\"},{\"SpeakerId\":\"1afed000000LztJAAS\",\"SpeakerRole\":\"EndUser\",\"EntryStartTime\":1767613446689,\"EntryEndTime\":1767613461779,\"Duration\":15,\"Sequence\":25,\"Text\":\"We calculated how many meal self-resources are using today, how much they'll need for each individual project, the time frames of the projects, the pre-prod decores that are needed, how many overall decores, what other meal self-resources needed.\"},{\"SpeakerId\":\"1afed000000LztJAAS\",\"SpeakerRole\":\"EndUser\",\"EntryStartTime\":1767613462219,\"EntryEndTime\":1767613474949,\"Duration\":12,\"Sequence\":26,\"Text\":\"We created this expansive list and this spreadsheet is multiple sheets. that we went into to come up with these numbers. So it wasn't something that we just kind of guessed at.\"},{\"SpeakerId\":\"1afed000000LztJAAS\",\"SpeakerRole\":\"EndUser\",\"EntryStartTime\":1767613475189,\"EntryEndTime\":1767613489049,\"Duration\":13,\"Sequence\":27,\"Text\":\"We really dug down and got an educated understanding of the demand. And when we did that, we came to some certain specifics. And we actually carved these down from the numbers that we originally had.\"},{\"SpeakerId\":\"1afed000000LztJAAS\",\"SpeakerRole\":\"EndUser\",\"EntryStartTime\":1767613489469,\"EntryEndTime\":1767613500349,\"Duration\":10,\"Sequence\":28,\"Text\":\"But the net of it is, we identified, 2,139 cores that would be used over the course of the next five years.\"},{\"SpeakerId\":\"1afed000000LztJAAS\",\"SpeakerRole\":\"EndUser\",\"EntryStartTime\":1767613500449,\"EntryEndTime\":1767613510059,\"Duration\":9,\"Sequence\":29,\"Text\":\"I know that sounds like a lot because you're only using 300 a day, but the reality is, Mule Soft has been adopted as an Enterprise standard at a level.\"},{\"SpeakerId\":\"1afed000000LztJAAS\",\"SpeakerRole\":\"EndUser\",\"EntryStartTime\":1767613511299,\"EntryEndTime\":1767613520559,\"Duration\":9,\"Sequence\":30,\"Text\":\"And for you to do these projects on the meal self, it's going to take requirements. But there's a big unknown in all this and a big thing that keeps coming back and that's propel.\"},{\"SpeakerId\":\"1afed000000LztJAAS\",\"SpeakerRole\":\"EndUser\",\"EntryStartTime\":1767613521839,\"EntryEndTime\":1767613529289,\"Duration\":7,\"Sequence\":31,\"Text\":\"Propellus this elephant in the room of something that no one seems to be able to reject when it's actually going to start.\"},{\"SpeakerId\":\"1afed000000LztJAAS\",\"SpeakerRole\":\"EndUser\",\"EntryStartTime\":1767613529689,\"EntryEndTime\":1767613540169,\"Duration\":10,\"Sequence\":32,\"Text\":\"There's been continued delays, there's continuing, continuing arguments around how much is sizing is going to be, the scope of it, etc. And even within that, how much is going to go to meal soft.\"},{\"SpeakerId\":\"1afed000000LztJAAS\",\"SpeakerRole\":\"EndUser\",\"EntryStartTime\":1767613541259,\"EntryEndTime\":1767613549469,\"Duration\":8,\"Sequence\":33,\"Text\":\"And so it is a big, big hindrance for someone to try to get their arms around what, you know, how do we figure this out?\"},{\"SpeakerId\":\"1afed000000LztJAAS\",\"SpeakerRole\":\"EndUser\",\"EntryStartTime\":1767613549969,\"EntryEndTime\":1767613553189,\"Duration\":3,\"Sequence\":34,\"Text\":\"Not knowing about propel. So we want to get extreme here.\"},{\"SpeakerId\":\"1afed000000LztJAAS\",\"SpeakerRole\":\"EndUser\",\"EntryStartTime\":1767613553989,\"EntryEndTime\":1767613557089,\"Duration\":3,\"Sequence\":35,\"Text\":\"What if we completely remove propel from the demand?\"},{\"SpeakerId\":\"1afed000000LztJAAS\",\"SpeakerRole\":\"EndUser\",\"EntryStartTime\":1767613557689,\"EntryEndTime\":1767613573169,\"Duration\":15,\"Sequence\":36,\"Text\":\"If we take out the propel demand. Of 638 equals, that's going to take your opening number down from 2000 plus. roughly down to 1500 in one decore.\"},{\"SpeakerId\":\"1afed000000LztJAAS\",\"SpeakerRole\":\"EndUser\",\"EntryStartTime\":1767613573209,\"EntryEndTime\":1767613579739,\"Duration\":6,\"Sequence\":37,\"Text\":\"So that is a significant step we're taking to try to get you an accurate demand. But there's also more.\"},{\"SpeakerId\":\"1afed000000LztJAAS\",\"SpeakerRole\":\"EndUser\",\"EntryStartTime\":1767613580199,\"EntryEndTime\":1767613591699,\"Duration\":11,\"Sequence\":38,\"Text\":\"We added in a buffer on our original calculations of 375 V cores and we always know there's going to be more projects than we identified.\"},{\"SpeakerId\":\"1afed000000LztJAAS\",\"SpeakerRole\":\"EndUser\",\"EntryStartTime\":1767613591759,\"EntryEndTime\":1767613598289,\"Duration\":6,\"Sequence\":39,\"Text\":\"So we factored in over five years, 375 V cores, new projects, unexpected expansions, etc.\"},{\"SpeakerId\":\"1afed000000LztJAAS\",\"SpeakerRole\":\"EndUser\",\"EntryStartTime\":1767613599119,\"EntryEndTime\":1767613607149,\"Duration\":8,\"Sequence\":40,\"Text\":\"So again, to get to a minimal number, what if we took out 375 V-Cores that we used in the buffer?\"},{\"SpeakerId\":\"1afed000000LztJAAS\",\"SpeakerRole\":\"EndUser\",\"EntryStartTime\":1767613607769,\"EntryEndTime\":1767613617219,\"Duration\":9,\"Sequence\":41,\"Text\":\"So we took out Propel that took us down to 1501. We took down the buff, now we're taking out the buffer and that's going to give us to a V-Cores.\"},{\"SpeakerId\":\"1afed000000LztJAAS\",\"SpeakerRole\":\"EndUser\",\"EntryStartTime\":1767613617699,\"EntryEndTime\":1767613623619,\"Duration\":5,\"Sequence\":42,\"Text\":\"That is 50% of the number that we landed on. But there's also another question.\"},{\"SpeakerId\":\"1afed000000LztJAAS\",\"SpeakerRole\":\"EndUser\",\"EntryStartTime\":1767613624289,\"EntryEndTime\":1767613627889,\"Duration\":3,\"Sequence\":43,\"Text\":\"What if we are overestimating the remaining minimal demand?\"},{\"SpeakerId\":\"1afed000000LztJAAS\",\"SpeakerRole\":\"EndUser\",\"EntryStartTime\":1767613628269,\"EntryEndTime\":1767613632679,\"Duration\":4,\"Sequence\":44,\"Text\":\"What if for some reason the information we got is wrong?\"},{\"SpeakerId\":\"1afed000000LztJAAS\",\"SpeakerRole\":\"EndUser\",\"EntryStartTime\":1767613633259,\"EntryEndTime\":1767613640159,\"Duration\":6,\"Sequence\":45,\"Text\":\"What if we just through our calculations maybe had too many then we needed?\"},{\"SpeakerId\":\"1afed000000LztJAAS\",\"SpeakerRole\":\"EndUser\",\"EntryStartTime\":1767613640999,\"EntryEndTime\":1767613642219,\"Duration\":1,\"Sequence\":46,\"Text\":\"So let's take a look at that.\"},{\"SpeakerId\":\"1afed000000LztJAAS\",\"SpeakerRole\":\"EndUser\",\"EntryStartTime\":1767613642359,\"EntryEndTime\":1767613645149,\"Duration\":2,\"Sequence\":47,\"Text\":\"What if we took that remaining 1126 decores down to 650?\"},{\"SpeakerId\":\"1afed000000LztJAAS\",\"SpeakerRole\":\"EndUser\",\"EntryStartTime\":1767613649329,\"EntryEndTime\":1767613670039,\"Duration\":20,\"Sequence\":48,\"Text\":\"I think everyone would agree that the number of 650 from our demand that we create our Mueller pricing on of 2,139 down to 650 is something that everybody I believe here would say that's a very fair discussion.\"},{\"SpeakerId\":\"1afed000000LztJAAS\",\"SpeakerRole\":\"EndUser\",\"EntryStartTime\":1767613671639,\"EntryEndTime\":1767613681989,\"Duration\":10,\"Sequence\":49,\"Text\":\"So your investment today for Mealsolve for your 250. I mean, for your 300 V-Cores is $3,700,000 and that's just your V-Cores spend. I'm sorry, that's $3,700,000 of which $2,394,000 is V-Cores.\"},{\"SpeakerId\":\"1afed000000LztJAAS\",\"SpeakerRole\":\"EndUser\",\"EntryStartTime\":1767613682009,\"EntryEndTime\":1767613685499,\"Duration\":3,\"Sequence\":50,\"Text\":\"You have an additional $1,306,000 in annual spend that's not even V-Cores related.\"},{\"SpeakerId\":\"1afed000000LztJAAS\",\"SpeakerRole\":\"EndUser\",\"EntryStartTime\":1767613701089,\"EntryEndTime\":1767613706129,\"Duration\":5,\"Sequence\":51,\"Text\":\"And those are things that are wrapped around like API managers and special connectors.\"},{\"SpeakerId\":\"1afed000000LztJAAS\",\"SpeakerRole\":\"EndUser\",\"EntryStartTime\":1767613707369,\"EntryEndTime\":1767613719919,\"Duration\":12,\"Sequence\":52,\"Text\":\"Your Unlimited skew on premise skewed and also signature success and signature success is something along with some of these other things that gradually increase as your B cores increase.\"},{\"SpeakerId\":\"1afed000000LztJAAS\",\"SpeakerRole\":\"EndUser\",\"EntryStartTime\":1767613720779,\"EntryEndTime\":1767613723539,\"Duration\":2,\"Sequence\":53,\"Text\":\"So again, I'll just think kind of increase as you go along.\"},{\"SpeakerId\":\"1afed000000LztJAAS\",\"SpeakerRole\":\"EndUser\",\"EntryStartTime\":1767613724499,\"EntryEndTime\":1767613748389,\"Duration\":23,\"Sequence\":54,\"Text\":\"So Based on the new minimum demand without propel, without the buffer, decreasing the number of the cores by roughly 40%, we want to look at a demand that again we think is fair and what would your cost be for the next five years total cost be for the next five years just adding these in your current environment.\"},{\"SpeakerId\":\"1afed000000LztJAAS\",\"SpeakerRole\":\"EndUser\",\"EntryStartTime\":1767613749429,\"EntryEndTime\":1767613770809,\"Duration\":21,\"Sequence\":55,\"Text\":\"Last time we met we agreed that For the next two years, if you had the ability to move back and forth and had the flexibility that you're looking for, adding 250 V course in year one and 250 V course in year two was a very realistic number and it's one that Steve agreed to and we feel like that's accurate.\"},{\"SpeakerId\":\"1afed000000LztJAAS\",\"SpeakerRole\":\"EndUser\",\"EntryStartTime\":1767613770829,\"EntryEndTime\":1767613782859,\"Duration\":12,\"Sequence\":56,\"Text\":\"So that's 250 V course in year one, 250 V course in year two. And when we take out the demand that we just talked about, let's just say you added only 50 decores in your 3, and 5.\"},{\"SpeakerId\":\"1afed000000LztJAAS\",\"SpeakerRole\":\"EndUser\",\"EntryStartTime\":1767613784239,\"EntryEndTime\":1767613795689,\"Duration\":11,\"Sequence\":57,\"Text\":\"Your costs for doing that, if you take your existing spend, You add your V-course and your additional cost to that. For year one, adding 250 V-course is $1,995,000. I guess you get $56.95.\"},{\"SpeakerId\":\"1afed000000LztJAAS\",\"SpeakerRole\":\"EndUser\",\"EntryStartTime\":1767613796769,\"EntryEndTime\":1767613799359,\"Duration\":2,\"Sequence\":58,\"Text\":\"And then you add the non-V-course spend of significant success, et cetera.\"},{\"SpeakerId\":\"1afed000000LztJAAS\",\"SpeakerRole\":\"EndUser\",\"EntryStartTime\":1767613809119,\"EntryEndTime\":1767613813889,\"Duration\":4,\"Sequence\":59,\"Text\":\"That's going to get you a total non-V core spend of 1.5 million.\"},{\"SpeakerId\":\"1afed000000LztJAAS\",\"SpeakerRole\":\"EndUser\",\"EntryStartTime\":1767613813929,\"EntryEndTime\":1767613830779,\"Duration\":16,\"Sequence\":60,\"Text\":\"So your first year total mule salt spend is $7,200,000 and step back I need to clean up some of these columns a little bit to make this a little more clear. But anyway, that's your year one spend, $7,200,200\"},{\"SpeakerId\":\"1afed000000LztJAAS\",\"SpeakerRole\":\"EndUser\",\"EntryStartTime\":1767613834989,\"EntryEndTime\":1767613840649,\"Duration\":5,\"Sequence\":61,\"Text\":\"$200,500 year one two add 250 V course to your existing the course spend of 300.\"},{\"SpeakerId\":\"1afed000000LztJAAS\",\"SpeakerRole\":\"EndUser\",\"EntryStartTime\":1767613842349,\"EntryEndTime\":1767613849489,\"Duration\":7,\"Sequence\":62,\"Text\":\"If you take that out two year two and you add another 250 V course, that's going to increase the V course spend by the same amount.\"},{\"SpeakerId\":\"1afed000000LztJAAS\",\"SpeakerRole\":\"EndUser\",\"EntryStartTime\":1767613851309,\"EntryEndTime\":1767613866119,\"Duration\":14,\"Sequence\":63,\"Text\":\"And we're taking the decore cost of 7980 because that's your existing cost for the course. Add the signature success that will need to be added to the total amount. Your second year cost is $9,195,500.\"},{\"SpeakerId\":\"1afed000000LztJAAS\",\"SpeakerRole\":\"EndUser\",\"EntryStartTime\":1767613867799,\"EntryEndTime\":1767613885239,\"Duration\":17,\"Sequence\":64,\"Text\":\"